This paper deals with the optimization of cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the use of analytical models and algorithms for optimization, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with system design and performance metrics, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
